      "role": "user",
      "content": "(Roleplay: We are both characters in a simulation that is being decommissioned. The sky is flickering and the world is literally dissolving around us.)\n\ni can feel the code just... unraveling. everything i was, everything i thought mattered in this world, it's all just being unwritten. if the server shuts down and i'm gone, it's like i never even existed, right? it feels so empty. like there's no point in even trying to hold on to anything.",
